messages.message:
Hi all, our very own @shaunak will be speaking at the upcoming Weaviate event. At this event, there will also be workshops in using Weaviate. Those interested can sign up below (free). The event takes place in San Francisco on March 21. More details on the sign up page. 

https://events.weaviate.io/ai-in-prod-sf-24 (https://events.weaviate.io/ai-in-prod-sf-24)
